Chaos/Minion:




Chaos waved a hand at Havoc.  "You there?" he looked to Minion and sighed.  
"Transform."

"Yes, sir." Minion transformed into his jet fighter mode, his cockpit 
flipping open.  The red and black jet awaited further instructions or action.

Chaos climbed up on the wing of Minion and then hopped into the cockpit, 
shutting it and sitting back as Minion blasted off, engines at full power, 
for the Cybertronian Fire.
